title: JD.com Unit to Start Trading in Hong Kong After $383 Million IPO
description: Jingdong Industrials Inc., the supply-chain unit of Chinese e-commerce giant JD.com Inc., is set to debut in Hong Kong on Thursday after its HK$2.98 billion ($383 million) offering.
